ッチやアンラップ記述を増やしやすい。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"leWUl","x":3576,"y":5460,"name":"L1-5::Group 63 :: Group 1 :: Lone 534 :: Lone 594 :: Sticky Note dr14:67","width":260,"fill":"#D5F5E3","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"xBEwe","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"REPLとライブ環境は探索作業の速度を上げる一方で試行エラー頻度を増やしやすい。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"K08Nx","x":3576,"y":3460,"name":"L1-5::Group 69 :: Group 1 :: Group 63 :: Group 63 :: Sticky Note dr2:46","width":260,"fill":"#FADBD8","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"ZPFEH","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"RustのPoloniusは将来性が高い一方でコンパイル時間や実装コストの課題を抱える。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"DYI6V","x":3292,"y":3460,"name":"L1-5::Group 69 :: Group 1 :: Group 63 :: Group 63 :: Sticky Note dr12:41","width":260,"fill":"#FADBD8","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"jUB3U","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"Poloniusは精度向上の代わりにコンパイル時間増加が課題となる。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"HwVHx","x":2724,"y":5660,"name":"L1-5::Group 83 :: Group 1 :: Lone 572 :: 