 API を提供する。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"n4io2","x":668,"y":10460,"name":"L1-7::Group 58 :: Group 1 :: Group 26 :: Group 22 :: Sticky Note dr3:60","width":260,"fill":"#D4EFDF","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"cgLiT","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"Java 21 の StructuredTaskScope は shutdown-on-failure などで高水準なキャンセル方針を表現できる。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"qvOlS","x":100,"y":10460,"name":"L1-7::Group 58 :: Group 1 :: Group 26 :: Group 22 :: Sticky Note dr13:65","width":260,"fill":"#D4EFDF","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"duDvY","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"StructuredTaskScopeは短絡失敗時の一括キャンセルを簡潔に記述できる。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"j5tKY","x":668,"y":3860,"name":"L1-7::Group 62 :: Group 1 :: Lone 167 :: Lone 186 :: Sticky Note dr2:36","width":260,"fill":"#FFD1DC","cornerRadius":4,"effect":{"type":"shadow","shadowType":"outer","color":"#00000026","offset":{"x":2,"y":4},"blur":10},"layout":"vertical","gap":16,"padding":[32,28,28,28],"children":[{"type":"text","id":"D0AY1","name":"body","fill":"#6B5900","textGrowth":"fixed-width","width":"fill_container","content":"SwiftのARCはランタイムGCを使わずコンパイル時挿入でretain/releaseを管理する。","lineHeight":1.6,"fontFamily":"Inter","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"normal"}],"enabled":false},{"type":"frame","id":"njBGm","x":668,"y":13660,"name":"L1